0:00:00.000,0:00:02.120
Mvura mvura dziri mukenza dzino Buda PAKAREPO Mushure Memunamato!!!

0:00:02.120,0:00:05.220
NGUVA YEKUPORESWA

0:00:05.220,0:00:08.860
Chiratidzo chawave kuzoona chine zvinobata mwoyo zvikuru

0:00:08.860,0:00:14.260
asi kunyange chingave chisina kukodzera kuti chionekwe ne munhu wese, ndechekupa kubwinya kuna Mwari.

0:00:14.260,0:00:19.080
Va Ganiu Sulaimon avo vane makore makumi maviri nemashanu vanobva ku Kwara Sate, Nigeria,

0:00:19.080,0:00:25.140
vasvika pa Synagogue Church of All Nations vaine dambudziko rekurwadziwa kwakanyanyisa kwazvo nekenza yepagumbo.

0:00:25.140,0:00:29.640
Anosimuka kubva pachigaro kuti aratidze nzvimbo chaiyo iyo kenza yakatanga.

0:00:29.640,0:00:33.360
Kamera inoswedera padyo kuti inyatsotora pikicha ye chironda chacho

0:00:33.360,0:00:38.500
Urikuona kuti ganda regumbo rake rose rakaora.

0:00:38.500,0:00:45.220
Kufufunuka kwe ganda rakafa; zviratidzo zvehutachiona hwekenza hwakapararira ne gumbo rake rerudyi

0:00:45.220,0:00:48.360
Aya mamiriro apfuura simba rezvisikwa,

0:00:48.360,0:00:53.160
kuti hakuna tekinoloji yezvokurapa kana mishonga inogona kugadzirisa dambudziko romurume uyu.

0:00:53.160,0:00:56.340
Zvinogona chete kurapwa, asi hazvikwanisi kuporeswa.

0:00:56.340,0:01:00.460
Dambudziko iri rava chituko, uye ndiani anogona kubvisa chituko?

0:01:00.460,0:01:03.460
Ndiani umwe kunze kwa Jesu Kristu

0:01:03.460,0:01:13.420
1 Petro 2:24 kusvika 25 inoti, "Akatakura zvitadzo zvedu mumuviri wake pamuti, kuti tife kune zvitadzo uye tigorarama mukururama."

0:01:13.420,0:01:15.820
Ne maronda ake, isu takaporeswa.

0:01:15.820,0:01:20.580
Va Ganiu Sulaimon vakamirira mukutenda mumutsetse wekunamatirwa pa Synagogue Church of All Nations

0:01:20.580,0:01:24.900
vachitenda kuti Jesu Kristu ndiye mumwe chete zuro, nhasi, nekusingaperi,

0:01:24.900,0:01:29.120
uye kuti kungosangana Naye kuburikidza nemuranda Wake, mu Porofita T.B. Joshua,

0:01:29.120,0:01:32.300
kuchaunza kuporesa kwakakwana muzita ra Jesu.

0:01:32.300,0:01:37.040
Mu Porofita T.B. Joshua asvika pamutsetse semunamato semutumwa wa Kristu,

0:01:37.040,0:01:41.520
kutumira chikumbiro cha Mwari kuburikidza naye, kuti Jesu Kristu ndiye nyanzvi yekuponesa,

0:01:41.520,0:01:44.660
uye kuti Anoporesa nekuda kwe ruponeso rwemweya yavo.

0:01:44.660,0:01:47.480
Muzita rakasimba ra Jesu Kristu!

0:01:47.480,0:01:51.740
Hurwa nezvinhu zvine chepfu izvo zvakanga zvakatsonyerwa pasi peganda,

0:01:51.740,0:01:56.700
pakarepo zvinotanga kubuda kubva mugumbo rake, nekuyerara pasi.

0:01:56.700,0:01:59.240
Chii chiri kuitika kuna Mr. Sulaimon?

0:01:59.240,0:02:02.180
Izvi zvinopfuura kunzwisisa kwevanhu.

0:02:02.180,0:02:06.460
Izvi zvinotsigira izvo Mupositori Pauro anoti muna 1 VaKorinte, chitsauko 2, ndima 4:

0:02:06.460,0:02:19.860
"Shoko rangu nokuparidza kwangu zvakanga zvisina mashoko okugombedzera nouchenjeri, asi nokuratidza kwesimba raMweya, kuti kutenda kwenyu kurege kuva kwouchenjeri hwavanhu, asi kuve kwesimba ra Mwari.

0:02:19.860,0:02:23.600
Mukadzi arikukunguruka pasi ndiye amai va Mr Ganiu Salaimon

0:02:23.600,0:02:27.040
vachifara pane zvaitwa na Jesu Kristu ku mwanakomana wavo.

0:02:27.040,0:02:35.380
Mr. Ganiu Salaimon vanotanga kufamba muchiedza cheuchapupu hwavo, vachipupurira kuti marwadzo aenda.

0:02:35.380,0:02:36.420
Hareruya!

0:02:36.420,0:02:40.740
Tarisai ku mukomana! Mukomana ari kufamba zvino; arikufamba zvakaisvonakisisa.

0:02:40.740,0:02:47.060
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Ishe Jesu

0:02:47.060,0:02:49.040
Kuna Mwari ngakuve ne Kubwinya!

0:02:49.040,0:02:55.780
Va Ganiu Salaimon vakaporeswa zvachose mushure mokugamuchira munyengetero kubva kumu Porofita T.B. Joshua muzita ra Jesu.

0:02:55.780,0:03:02.400
Ndinokutendai, Jesu.

0:03:02.400,0:03:07.460
Mr Ganiu Salaimon naamai vavo vanofamba sevakundi vachiteedza mutsetse wekunamatirwa

0:03:07.460,0:03:13.380
vachipa kutenda kuna Jesu Kristu nokuda kwesimba Rake rokuporesa ne kununura

0:03:13.380,0:03:16.540
Ndiani akafanana na Jesu? Ndiani akafanana na She?

0:03:16.540,0:03:19.840
Hakuna zvachose hakuna munhu akafanana na Jesu Kristu.

0:03:19.840,0:03:27.080
Kuruboshwe, taona Va Ganiu Salaimon vachitambura nechinetso chikuru chekenza yegumbo, asi kurudyi,

0:03:27.080,0:03:30.860
unoona ganda ra Va Ganiu Salaimon radzorerwa zvachose

0:03:30.860,0:03:35.280
mushure mokugamuchira munyengetero kubva ku mu Porofita T.B. Joshua muzita ra Jesu.

0:03:35.280,0:03:44.720
Gumbo ravo raive noutano hwakakwana.

0:03:44.720,0:03:48.320
Vachirova rova nzvimbo iyo kenza yegumbo yaimbova,

0:03:48.320,0:03:53.780
Va Ganiu Salaimon vanopupurira kuti havachanzwa kurwadziwa.

0:03:53.780,0:03:59.380
NGUVA YE UCHAPUPU

0:03:59.380,0:04:05.940
Dambudziko rakandisvitsa pano nhasi raiva re kenza yegumbo.

0:04:05.940,0:04:12.440
Ndakaenda kune zvipatara zvakawanda, asi zvose zvakashaya basa.

0:04:12.440,0:04:16.460
Handaikwanisa kufamba, kumira, kana kuenda kuchimbuzi ndoga.

0:04:16.460,0:04:25.020
Ndaifanira kutakurwa kuenda kunozvibatsira.

0:04:25.020,0:04:33.540
Apo kurwadziwa kwakanga kusasaite, ndakarasikirwa netariro yokuti ndaizombofamba zvakare.

0:04:33.540,0:04:38.580
Pandakasvika pa S.C.O.A.N, mu Porofita T.B. Joshua akatambanudza ruoko rwake kune gumbo rangu akandinamatira.

0:04:38.580,0:04:41.280
Akandiudza kuti ndisimuke.

0:04:41.280,0:04:46.100
Pakarepo, rakaputika uye zvose zvekenza zvakatanga kubuda kubva mugumbo rangu.

0:04:46.100,0:04:53.580
Mr Ganiu Salaimon anokwidza mudhebhe wake ne kupupura kuti Jesu Kristu akamusunungura.

0:04:53.580,0:04:57.540
Anorova zvakare nzvimbo iyo kenza yegumbo yaimbova,

0:04:57.540,0:04:59.520
Mr. Ganiu Salaimon: Hapana marwadzo; Ndasununguka zvino.

0:04:59.520,0:05:02.600
Kuratidza kuti akaporeswa.

0:05:02.600,0:05:05.300
Anoti hapana marwadzo.

0:05:05.300,0:05:09.900
Ichi chisimbiso chokuti Vhangeri ra Jesu Kristu ichokwadi isimba ra Mwari

0:05:09.900,0:05:14.440
kuitira ruponeso rweumwe neumwe anotenda. VaRoma 1: 6.

